


#  Netflix Data Analysis using Python

##  Project Overview
This project performs Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on Netflixâ€™s movies and TV shows dataset to uncover insights about content distribution, growth trends, genre popularity, and country-wise production.

---

##  Dataset
- Source: Netflix Movies and TV Shows Dataset
- Format: CSV
- Records: Movies and TV Shows available on Netflix till 2021

