## Key Questions Answered
- What is the distribution of Movies vs TV Shows on Netflix?
- How has Netflix content grown over the years?
- Which countries produce the most Netflix content?
- What are the most popular genres on Netflix?
- What is the typical duration of Netflix movies and TV shows?

---

## Key Insights
- Netflixâ€™s catalog is dominated by movies.
- Content production increased rapidly after 2015.
- The USA and India are the top content-producing countries.
- Drama and International Movies are the most popular genres.
- Most Netflix movies are between 80â€“120 minutes long.
- TV shows usually have 1â€“2 seasons, indicating a focus on short-series formats.


